# ============================================================================
# DOCUMENTATION POLICY - Enterprise Standards
# ============================================================================
# Only professional, enterprise-standard documentation is allowed in the repo
# All development notes, guides, and internal docs must be gitignored
#
# ALLOWED DOCUMENTATION (Enterprise Standard):
#   - README.md              - Project overview and quick start
#   - API_DOCUMENTATION.md   - REST API reference 
#   - USER_GUIDE.md          - Comprehensive usage guide
#   - DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md     - Contributing and development guide
#   - CONFIGURATION_REFERENCE.md - Configuration schema documentation
#   - SECURITY_GUIDE.md      - Security best practices
#   - CONTRIBUTING.md        - Contribution guidelines
#   - CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md     - Community standards
#   - LICENSE                - Project license
#
# All other markdown files are excluded from version control
# ============================================================================

